57
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,180
Boring.

58
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,660
She isn't as weak as you think she is.

59
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,740
Take back your sword.

60
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:33,900
Don't be nervous.

61
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,100
Now, we're not enemies,

62
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,620
but friends.

63
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:49,740
You always trust people.

64
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,180
The Princess of the Spirit clan

65
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,420
is the heir of the Spirit Queen.

66
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,300
When the Spirit clan is rebuilt,

67
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,180
she'll be a queen

68
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:59,580
instead of a canary kept in your palace.

69
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,620
Saya, don't forget.

70
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,860
Today, you're leaving for your own clan.

71
00:05:09,260 --> 00:05:09,900
Lingzhi,

72
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:12,180
would you like to travel to my clan?

73
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:16,980
General, why don't you leave off early?

74
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,180
My consort

75
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:21,060
will certainly stay with me.

76
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,460
Your Majesty, you get nervous, too.

77
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:29,140
Looks like however foxy a man is,

78
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,700
he'll be obsessed with love.

79
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:35,300
It's a long journey.

80
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:36,900
Take care, General.

81
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:40,100
We'll meet again.

82
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:41,780
I should go.

83
00:05:58,660 --> 00:05:59,900
Do I have to

84
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,500
live in this palace all my life?

85
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,820
Your Grace, the Snow King
is here to see you.

86
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:14,460
There you are.

87
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,220
Let's get in.

88
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:30,580
Sorry.

89
00:06:34,540 --> 00:06:36,020
Are you thinking of leaving the palace?

90
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:46,500
I can't leave for the moment.

91
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,860
Mu Xuanjue just got back his power

92
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:49,980
with a shaky foundation.

93
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,860
I should stay and help him.

94
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:54,500
This is the excuse you find for yourself

95
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,580
and this is what upsets you.

96
00:06:59,220 --> 00:06:59,900
Maybe

97
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:02,060
you don't belong here.

98
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:04,820
Snow King, you just never stop

99
00:07:04,820 --> 00:07:06,180
