100
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,500
If you feel unhappy to stay here,

101
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:09,980
I can take you away at any time.

102
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:15,020
If you want to leave,

103
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:16,540
I will hold a grand ceremony

104
